milestones.description: Yashpal Sharma has broken the record for most sixes (4) in ODIs for IND, going past Kapil Dev's 3
Yashpal Sharma has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for IND, going past Kapil Dev's 3
Jeremy Coney has broken the record for most catches (9) in ODIs for NZ, going past John Parker's 8
Mark Burgess and Lance Cairns's 79-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 54 between Jeremy Coney and Warren Lees
Chauhan and Yashpal Sharma's 65-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 58 between Viswanath and Gavaskar
